					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1163706#post-2264167</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1163706/the-space-soldier#post-2264167</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 05 Apr 2015 01:20:38 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>TwistedGears</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1735681</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>It's moderately entertaining, if very standard Pesterbot humor, but the ending/rocket is such a massive plothole I can't help but downvote.</p> <p>The parents can't afford a toy soldier robot thing, but they can buy a rocket <em>capable of interstellar travel</em>? And, despite enjoying Pesterbot, the boy loads him into this rocket to go away forever. Just to try to shoehorn Pesterbot into being this alien toything.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
